Subject: [PATCH] cls_matchall: avoid panic when receiving a packet before
 filter set
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.1.9
Git-commit: 25426043ec9e22b90c789407c28e40f32a9d1985

[ Upstream commit 25426043ec9e22b90c789407c28e40f32a9d1985 ]

